Description: P2P Platform Server Components
 P2P Platform provides STUN, TURN relay, signaling, and DID services
 for peer-to-peer communication infrastructure.
 .
 This package includes:
  - STUN server for NAT traversal
  - TURN relay server for fallback connectivity
  - WebRTC signaling server
  - Decentralized Identity (DID) service
